Breakdown on what Ella’s color….
We’ve been taking a natural/healthier route to her hair by essentially growing out her blonde and letting her natural color grow in and glossing her a warm golden honey tone, this appointment specifically we were feeling that a little dimension and brighter pops needed to come in! We blended go through her whole head doing babylights with a soft “money piece “ effect to brighten, reblend, and contour to bring her look back to life!  Glossed with @redken #shadeseq 8gi 8wg 8v and root melted with 6n 6NCh
